                        <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/rebrand/icns/so-sure_icon_holding-phone.png" alt="so-sure - Be careful" width="180px">
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-primary">Be Careful</h5>
                    <p class="mb-5 text-zaffre">Easy as that, don't break or lose your phone, or make any claims throughout the policy year. Oh, and make sure your connections do the same</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="intro__step">
                        <div class="intro__number d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h4 text-primary">3</div>
                        <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/rebrand/icns/so-sure_icon_reward-pot.png" alt="so-sure - Get Rewarded" width="180px">
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-primary">Get Rewarded</h5>
                    <p class="mb-2 text-zaffre">At the end of the year, when you and your connections havenâ€™t claimed, your
