                       data-cardbox-anchor="#what-is-the-reward-pot-text">Reward Pot</a>
                    is paid out to you</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block-xs mt-3 get-a-quote">Get Insured in minutes</a>
